						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Launch-of-the-first-scientific-cooperation-programme-Africa-Brazil-France-to-fight-desertification-in-Africa" title="Launch of the first scientific cooperation programme Africa-Brazil-France to fight desertification in Africa" alt="link">Launch of the first scientific cooperation programme Africa-Brazil-France to fight desertification in Africa</a></h2>

	
					<p>Launch of the first scientific cooperation programme Africa-Brazil-France to fight desertification in Africa&nbsp;This scientific programme is an original South-South-North cooperation initiative, jointly financed by Brazil, Africa and France. It aims to structure a scientific community comprised of African, Brazilian and French researchers to fight desertification in Africa, build scientific capacities on this continent and strengthen links between science and society, in order to contribute to a sustainable management of arid and semi-arid areas in Africa.(IRD, 4/6/2012)EN: http://en.ird.fr/all-the-current-events/news/press-releases/rio-20-ird-and-aird-join-forces&nbsp;FR: http://www.ird.fr/toute-l-actualite/actualites/communiques-et-dossiers-de-presse/rio-20-l-ird-et-l-aird-se-mobilisent&nbsp;</p>
							<p><span class="date">24/09/2012</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Launch-of-the-first-scientific-cooperation-programme-Africa-Brazil-France-to-fight-desertification-in-Africa">Read more...</a>
</div>
<br class="cl">
